    |
    |
    div(class="template-section m-a")
        |
        section(class="template-content u-animationFadeDown" ng-show="s_actividad == 1")

            h5  Watch the following videos, pay attention to the activities described by each person:

            div(class="row row-flex mt30 align-items-center")

                div(class="col xs12 md6")
                    div(class="row-flex justify-center mb20"): div(class="col md11 col-center")
                        div(class='c-contVideo')
                            video(controls class='u-responsive-video' poster="./../assets/multimedia/images/app/UNAD_video-poster.png")
                                source(src="unit_1/module_1/"+pathVideo+"col_3_1.mp4" type="video/mp4")
                                | Your browser does not support the audio element.
                div(class="col xs12 md6")
                    div(class="row-flex justify-center mb20"): div(class="col md11 col-center")
                        div(class='c-contVideo')
                            video(controls class='u-responsive-video' poster="./../assets/multimedia/images/app/UNAD_video-poster.png")
                                source(src='unit_1/module_1/'+pathVideo+'col_3_2.mp4' type='video/mp4')
                                | Your browser does not support the audio element.

            div(class="row row-flex mt30 align-items-center")

                div(class="col xs12 md6")
                    div(class="row-flex justify-center mb20"): div(class="col md11 col-center")
                        div(class='c-contVideo')
                            video(controls class='u-responsive-video' poster="./../assets/multimedia/images/app/UNAD_video-poster.png")
                                source(src="unit_1/module_1/"+pathVideo+"col_3_3.mp4" type="video/mp4")
                                | Your browser does not support the audio element.
                div(class="col xs12 md6")
                    div(class="row-flex justify-center mb20"): div(class="col md11 col-center")
                        div(class='c-contVideo')
                            video(controls class='u-responsive-video' poster="./../assets/multimedia/images/app/UNAD_video-poster.png")
                                source(src='unit_1/module_1/'+pathVideo+'col_3_4.mp4' type='video/mp4')
                                | Your browser does not support the audio element.
        |
        section(class="template-content u-animationFadeDown" ng-show="s_actividad == 2")
            h5 From the videos of informal jobs that we previously looked at, which ones do you believe will no longer exist in the near future?

            div(class="row row-flex mt30 align-items-center justify-center")
                div(class="row-flex col xs12 sm6 col-center")
                    figure.padding5.xs6: img(class='u-responsive-img' src="unit_1/module_1/"+pathImage+"col_3_5.png", alt='activities described by each person')
                    figure.padding5.xs6: img(class='u-responsive-img' src="unit_1/module_1/"+pathImage+"col_3_6.png", alt='activities described by each person')
                    figure.padding5.xs6: img(class='u-responsive-img' src="unit_1/module_1/"+pathImage+"col_3_7.png", alt='activities described by each person')
                    figure.padding5.xs6: img(class='u-responsive-img' src="unit_1/module_1/"+pathImage+"col_3_8.png", alt='activities described by each person')
                div(class="col xs12 sm6 col-center")
                    div(class="c-wrapTextarea ")
                        textarea(placeholder="Write here..." class="campo c-textarea h200" ng-model="textousuario")

